00:51.919 --> 01:03.397 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: They're still
searching
tonight for the man behind the
latest terror

01:03.430 --> 01:05.198 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
