potentially
a drawn-out fight over some of
these Cabinet

12:37.824 --> 12:39.158 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
nominees.

12:39.192 --> 12:40.760 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Let's talk
about the ACA
there in particular.

12:40.793 --> 12:42.428 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
How is that going to look?

12:42.462 --> 12:47.000 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMY WALTER: Well, that's really
-- we all
are going, well, nobody quite
knows.

12:47.033 --> 12:49.369 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Even Republicans don't quite
know.

12:49.402 --> 12:54.641 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
