Act.

14:06.746 --> 14:11.050 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There are people who have gotten
expanded
Medicaid, even in Republican
states.

14:11.084 --> 14:15.521 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And you have seen some
Republican senators
say things like, well, we don't
want -- let's

14:15.555 --> 14:17.623 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
