perhaps this week on paper...

14:53.826 --> 14:55.161 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: On a delay.

14:55.194 --> 14:56.629 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: ... but then
