point, move on
its own.

27:09.228 --> 27:14.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: President
Obama used this
fairly old act, the Antiquities
Act, to designate

27:14.399 --> 27:15.534 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
