27:15.567 --> 27:17.703 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Are these on pretty good legal
footing going
forward?

27:17.736 --> 27:19.471 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JULIET EILPERIN: Yes.

27:19.505 --> 27:22.774 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One of the things that's really
interesting
